## ğŸ“‚ Exemple minimal

```python
from PyCgame import PyCgame

def update():
    if PyCgame.touche_presser("Espace"):
        print("Espace pressÃ©e !")

PyCgame.init(largeur=160, hauteur=90, fps=60, update_func=update)
```

